<plot>The first of three anthologies based on the different stages of love. This first anthology (of 3 plays) focuses on new relationships, and was followed by _Out of Love (1974) (TV)_ (qv) which were 4 plays focusing on the breakdown of marriages, and Separate Ways which were 3 plays focusing on divorce.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?604910</url></doc>
